Let $G$ be a group, let $n \in \mathbb{N}$, let $\{A_i\}_{i \in I}$ be a directed family of $n$-generated subgroups, and set $A \defeq \langle A_i \rangle_{i \in I}$. Then $d(\widehat{A}) \leq n$.

